markets.title: How high will Bitcoin get this year?
markets.subtitle: $100,000 or above
markets.rules_primary: If the average of CF Benchmarks' Bitcoin Real-Time Index (BRTI) in a sixty minute period between 8AM and 7PM, excluding the top 20% and bottom 20% of values on weekdays (save stock market holidays) is above 99999.99 by Nov 22, 2024, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The Contract is settled by taking an average of CF Benchmarks' Bitcoin Real-Time Index (BRTI) in a sixty minute period between 8AM and 7PM, excluding the top 20% and bottom 20% of values. Importantly, only data used between 8AM and 7PM on weekdays are used (save stock market holidays) to resolve the contract.
markets.early_close_condition: If this event occurs, the market will close the following 10am ET.
